OL,3,C'Culture of fear' at hospital where
OL,4,Cjunior surgeons assaulted, report finds
OL,6,FBosses at University Hospitals Sussex
OL,7,FNHS Foundation Trust, which runs the
OL,8,Fhospital, commissioned the
OL,9,Finvestigation into its surgery
OL,10,Fservices which took place in May 2023.
OL,12,FThe Royal College of Surgeons flagged
OL,13,Fserious concerns between surgical
OL,14,Fstaff and the trust's senior
OL,15,Fleadership and said whistleblowers
OL,16,Fwere poorly treated, such as by being
OL,17,Fbullied or subjected to disciplinary
OL,18,Faction.
