OL,4,Cjunior surgeons assaulted, report finds
OL,6,FThey said: "There were concerning
OL,7,Freports of bullying by members of the
OL,8,Fexecutive leadership team, with
OL,9,Finstances of confrontational meetings
OL,10,Fwith individual consultant surgeons,
