OL,4,Cjunior surgeons assaulted, report finds
OL,6,F"It is imperative that robust action
OL,7,Fis taken to tackle unacceptable
OL,8,Fbehaviours, given the reports of
OL,9,Fbullying, harassment and physical
OL,10,Fabuse."
