OL,4,Cjunior surgeons assaulted, report finds
OL,6,FThe trust's chief executive Dr George
OL,7,FFindlay said he asked for this
OL,8,Findependent report because of the
OL,9,F"huge challenges" the surgery teams
OL,10,Fhave faced over many years and that
OL,11,Fall trust staff are focused on
OL,12,Fimproving care.
OL,14,FDr Findlay said: "Since last May when
OL,15,Fthe review took place, major changes
OL,16,Fhave begun ` we have invested in extra
OL,17,Fstaff and are recruiting now, we are
OL,18,Fseeking more theatre and bed capacity,
OL,19,Fand we have approved the opening of a
OL,20,FSurgical Assessment Unit.
